name: Picnic VIP Red Carpet Premier and After party tickets
description: Picnic VIP Red Carpet Premier and After party tickets will not be available at the door. Buy yours now to avoid crowds and missing out. The Picnic VIP Red Carpet Premier and After parties are expected to sell out before the dates because of the high quality of the acting and cinematography and the rising popularity of Picnic. The VIP Red Carpet Premier and After parties will be held in Nambour, Brisbane, Gold Coast, Newcastle, Sydney and Melbourne at venues and dates to be announced. Dress glamorous, come and have your photo taken on the red carpet, mingle/network, and be entertained. The entertainment at the After parties will be a band from the Picnic soundtrack.
